originalText.text: This was the best dental experience I have ever had! The front desk person Melly was welcoming and kind, and Dr Schick and his assistant were equally kind and attentive, friendly and caring. Dr Schick is energetic and thorough, he used warm water on my sensitive teeth (so comfortable)and the polish was not candy flavored, which was very pleasant. I would give this office 10 stars if I could.

originalText.text: I went to this office for 2 years and Robert Shick was the head dentist for at least one visit. I had a dental issue which they made an attempt to treat but didn't do a good job and the issue still bothered me. I recently went to a new dentist now that I live in Brooklyn who realized the issue right away. It's been a few weeks and I'm all good, this new dentist is clearly much better than here. My new dentist was shocked they didn't use novocaine on me. I thought Shick was ok, but after having better case, I realize I was wrong.
